{"tid":994350,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得父母真係老啦？","createTime":"2019-01-24T15:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T22:59:47.000Z","uid":19386,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d41aa0405520b24f9516a756d0c4db7adac2198c","tid":994350,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"每當一諗到未來十年左右就會再見唔到父母，就開始有D唔開心。有時仲諗，唔好彩可能十年都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算有，D病痛都開始出晒嚟，生活上好多細節都會唔同左<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢個係幾乎每個人都會經歷既事，但自己心態仲未tune到，有冇過來人講講點樣接受呢個人生巨大變化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66efb67c86d263e9ca4800529e2f0f518746d59","tid":994350,"uid":105888,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爸爸媽媽我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e4408d038de09f06f133c9eac29f08c86bb40a","tid":994350,"uid":19386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a66efb67c86d263e9ca4800529e2f0f518746d59","tid":994350,"uid":105888,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爸爸媽媽我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:30:51.000Z","msg":"如果愛父母，真係要珍惜每一日相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過人生就係無論幾珍惜，終結一日都會嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffcd7fcdb275771ef47ad1614ce740f12b7f271","tid":994350,"uid":221463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:32:04.000Z","msg":"唉，我都好驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face